### Responsibilities:
- Grow and develop new sales leads and build customer portfolio.
- Utilize technology resources and business relationships to achieve sales.
- Approach tasks in a detailed and organized fashion.
- Achieve growth and maximize income potential.
- Expand already established client base by proactively targeting key industries.
- Meet all KPI's and generate revenue for the region.
- Utilize existing relationships and network effectively to develop relationships and win business.

### Skills: 
- Energetic and dynamic.
- Self-directed, self-driven with entrepreneurial attitude.
- Ability to work in highly autonomous environment.
- Organized and detail-oriented.
- Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal.
- Ability to hunt down and source new business.
- Proven record of exceeding sales targets within competitive sector.
- Experience in the Forwarding industry including Sales and Operational experience.
- Sound knowledge of all facets of the end-to-end Freight Forwarding services.

